Here are both approaches for passing data to `ProductDetailsPage` and receiving it via `IQueryAttributable`.

## 1. Register the route

```csharp
// AppShell.xaml.cs
public AppShell()
{
    InitializeComponent();
    Routing.RegisterRoute("productdetails", typeof(ProductDetailsPage));
}
```

## 2. Navigate from ProductListPage

```csharp
// Approach A — string query parameter
async void OnProductSelected(Product product)
{
    await Shell.Current.GoToAsync($"productdetails?id={product.Id}");
}

// Approach B — pass the full object via ShellNavigationQueryParameters
async void OnProductSelected(Product product)
{
    var parameters = new ShellNavigationQueryParameters
    {
        { "product", product }
    };
    await Shell.Current.GoToAsync("productdetails", parameters);
}
```

## 3. Receive data in the ViewModel

```csharp
public class ProductDetailsViewModel : ObservableObject, IQueryAttributable
{
    private string _productId;
    private Product _product;

    public string ProductId
    {
        get => _productId;
        set => SetProperty(ref _productId, value);
    }

    public Product Product
    {
        get => _product;
        set => SetProperty(ref _product, value);
    }

    public void ApplyQueryAttributes(IDictionary<string, object> query)
    {
        // Approach A — string id passed via query string
        if (query.TryGetValue("id", out var id))
        {
            ProductId = id.ToString();
            // Load the full product from a service using ProductId
        }

        // Approach B — full object passed via ShellNavigationQueryParameters
        if (query.TryGetValue("product", out var obj) && obj is Product product)
        {
            Product = product;
        }
    }
}
```

**Key points:**

- **Approach A** serializes the ID into the URI — good for simple values and deep-link support.
- **Approach B** uses `ShellNavigationQueryParameters` — avoids serialization and preserves the full object graph, but doesn't support deep linking.
- Always `await` `GoToAsync` to avoid race conditions.
- The ViewModel must implement `IQueryAttributable`; Shell calls `ApplyQueryAttributes` automatically after navigation.
